@NODE ABOUT "Program Features..."
o	  Fast execution.

o	  Uses small amount of floppy and hard drive space.

o	  User customizable head and tail banners.

o	  Ability to print list (Local Only!)

o	  Three archiving formats to choose from for downloading list.

o	  Creates archives automatically at a sysop specified time and date.

o	  Ability to edit or kill an entry from list.

o	  Optional BBS ad for each entry.
          (Ads may contain ANSI, ASCII, or MCI codes and should be no bigger
          than 80x22).

o	  Local file transfers.

o	  Optionally uses PMK's wait.rexx program.
@ENDNODE
